freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I had severe alcohol intolerance last night. I was extremely intoxicated after my evening cocktail last night, which I usually tolerate with no symptoms at all. In fact I can often tolerate quite a bit more than 1 cocktail before I feel a bit tipsy, but last night was a something that I havent experienced since college.Just thought Id mention it. Who knows if its cause and effect.
